{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/portfolio/llama-as-a-service/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"02f98d78-ad99-5c6d-aee6-bf26b57ac94c","html":"<p>Random Llama Image API. The world's first Llama as a Service (LaaS) - by @spencerlepine</p>\n<p>This is a simple Node/Express REST API deployed to Heroku with GitHub Actions. It connects to the MongoDB NoSQL database, which stores image URL strings.</p>\n<p>Check out the Image API source code on <a href=\"https://github.com/llama-as-a-service/images-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<p>Originally, the goal of this project was to create a dockerized microservice architecture, with a gateway API and JWT authentintication. As you may suspect, this is an overly-complex solution for a simple REST API. I ran into a lot of issues working with Kubernetes, and have since left the project as is.</p>\n<p>To keep development of each service organized, I used the polyrepo approach with everything organized under the <a href=\"https://github.com/llama-as-a-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub Organization</a>.</p>\n<h4>‚úÖ Try It Out:</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> https://llama-as-a-service-images.herokuapp.com/random</code></pre></div>\n<h5>JSON Response</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://images.theconversation.com/files/337593/original/file-20200526-106811-ql6d51.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&amp;q=45&amp;auto=format&amp;w=1200&amp;h=900.0&amp;fit=crop\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>üé• Walkthrough Video</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uDQUA_JTMJk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/60903378/178522554-bdd1e702-b01c-4433-8d11-2b8e4ccf4f75.png\" alt=\"YouTube Video\"></a></p>\n<h2>üí° Blog Post</h2>\n<p>Read about the development process and what I learned on my <a href=\"https://www.spencerlepine.com/blog/building-llama-as-a-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">blog post</a></p>\n<h3>üõ†Ô∏è Built with:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js</li>\n<li>Express</li>\n<li>Docker</li>\n<li>Heroku</li>\n<li>GitHub Actions</li>\n<li>MongoDB</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>Also find me here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpencerLepine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter (@spencerlepine)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/spencerlepine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub (@spencerlepine)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/spencer-lepine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Llama as a Service","tech":["Node.js","MongoDB","GitHub Actions","Heroku"],"github":"https://github.com/llama-as-a-service/images-service","external":"https://llama-as-a-service.netlify.app/","description":"The world's first Llama as a Service (LaaS). A random llama image API built with NodeJS and MongoDB","slug":"/portfolio/llama-as-a-service","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5957446808510638,"src":"/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/8c332/laas-thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/95f17/laas-thumbnail.png 150w,\n/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/37d5a/laas-thumbnail.png 300w,\n/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/8c332/laas-thumbnail.png 600w,\n/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/03620/laas-thumbnail.png 900w,\n/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/6050d/laas-thumbnail.png 1200w,\n/static/5df8f0d4da24c42d43fd588b9ab47ed9/c86a3/laas-thumbnail.png 1258w","sizes":"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"}}}},"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/notspencer/workplace/portfolio-site-v2/content/portfolio/llama-as-a-service/llama-as-a-service.md"}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["1994492073"]}